OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMI5 spy reveals secret     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'unauthorised' IRA talks   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An MI5 spy who helped bring peace to   
OL,6, Northern Ireland by defying orders, has
OL,7, broken his silence to the BBC.         
OL,9,FHe has revealed he met IRA leaders in  
OL,10,FMarch 1993, despite talks being called 
OL,11,Foff by the British government after IRA
OL,12,Fbombs killed two young boys in England.
OL,14,FWhat he said in that meeting encouraged
OL,15,Fthem to declare the ceasefire and move 
OL,16,Ftowards the process that eventually led
OL,17,Fto the 1998 Good Friday Agreement.     
OL,19,FThe BBC's Peter Taylor has been trying 
OL,20,Fto find the spy for almost 30 years.   
OL,23,D]G     From the BBC News Website       
